precept Test

field test as quantity of 'mass' max '5 kg'
field test2 as integer max 2 optional default 2
field test3 as quantity of 'count' max 4

state offState initial
state onState terminal

event toggle initial

in offState omit test

from offState on toggle 
    -> set test = '{test2} [lb_av]'
    -> set test3 = '5 box'
    -> transition onState

